vice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-19T19:10:04Z to 2025-06-19T19:25:04Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 19:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-19 19:25:04+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "frontend-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "log_analysis_findings": "根据收集到的日志数据，以下是关于故障的初步信息：\n\n### 主要观察点\n从日志揭示的信息来看，错误集中在日志中提及的以下服务：\n1. **Frontend Service**\n2. **ProductCatalogService**\n\n多个日志条目中的错误均推荐产品或检索产品时出现问题，且错误涉及到以下关键词：\n- `failed to get recommended product info`\n- `could not retrieve product`\n- `rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n\n此外，某些日志明确指出的是数据库区域不可用问题。\n\n### 初步解析\n这些关键错误信息表明了问题有可能来自于区域错误或与相关服务之间的远程调用问题。\n\n现在我将对数据进行进一步分析，从中提取异常调用链和具体证据。\n通过对日志的进一步扫描，以下是显著的异常调用相关信息：\n\n### Detected Keywords\n从日志中提取到的显著关键词有：\n- `Region is unavailable`\n- `rpc error`\n- `failed to get recommended product info`\n- `failed to query product by id`\n\n这些关键词的出现频率较高，几乎都集中在 Frontend 和 ProductCatalogService 之间。\n\n### 分析结果\n1. **ProductCatalogService as Root Cause**:\n   - 高频日志 (出现 148 次) 显示产出异常根因可能是 `ProductCatalogService` 的区域不可用问题。例如日志消息 `failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`。\n\n2. **Frontend Issue Traces**:\n   - 调用链显示 Frontend 服务频繁地请求产品推荐及产品信息，但由于 ProductCatalogService 提供的信息不可用，因此报错。例如：日志消息 `failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`。\n\n### JSON格式结果输出：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"Region is unavailable\",\n    \"rpc error\",\n    \"failed to get recommended product info\",\n    \"failed to query product by id\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region reports unavailable, causing cascading errors in dependent calls.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Attempts to fetch product data and recommendations failed due to rpc errors pointing to unavailable region.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**下一步建议**:\n我建议进一步检查 ProductCatalogService，特别是其与区域相关的数据库配置及可用性。同时，验证当前其依赖的区域资源是否有突发故障记录。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据收集的指标数据进行分析，以下是问题识别结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"failed_query_ops\", \"duration_99th\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"failed_query_ops 和 duration_99th 指标异常，意味着数据库查询失败率增加和延迟时间显著上升。这可能导致服务响应能力下降。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed_query_ops 从 0 增加到 42.67，duration_99th 从 0.01 增加到 64.85。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"productcatalogservice 的 rrt 显著上升，可能因为后端数据库响应延迟，影响了服务性能。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1 的 rrt 从 7362.61 增加到 20129787.5。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"server_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 在 frontend 服务上升高，表明前端服务遇到了更多错误请求，可能受其他服务异常影响。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0 的 server_error_ratio 从 0.0 增加到 27.27。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析总结\n- TiDB 数据库的失败查询操作数和延迟显著升高，这可能是问题的核心原因，导致上游服务如 productcatalogservice 的响应时间也急剧上升。\n- 前端服务（frontend）出现高比例的错误请求，说明它受到了数据库性能问题的影响。 \n\n这种故障可能需要对 TiDB 数据库进行深入检查，并优化资源配置，以缓解查询失败和延迟问题。接下来，建议对数据库连接池配置等进行复查以降低故障影响。", "trace_analysis_findings": "已成功收集到异常调用链的分析数据，并完成初步数据解析。以下是发现的显著异常点和相关延迟/错误信息：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\", \n    \"productcatalogservice->TiDB\", \n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"timeout\", \n    \"region_unavailable_error\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"延迟和错误最显著的服务；交互中发现显著的地区不可用错误。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用路径 'productcatalogservice->TiDB' 延迟倍数约 4000 倍，错误状态为 Region is unavailable。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"依赖 productcatalogservice 的依赖路径延迟显著。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用路径 'checkoutservice->productcatalogservice' 延迟显著；均发生 Region is unavailable 错误。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend 与 productcatalogservice 的交互中出现显著超时。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用路径 'frontend->productcatalogservice' 的 HTTP 500 错误状态数量较高，且均与 Region is unavailable 错误有关。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 主要发现和分析：\n1. **关键瓶颈**:\n   - `ProductCatalogService` 是整个调用链中延迟的主要来源，延迟高达正常值的 4000 倍，同时大量报错 `Region is unavailable`。根本原因可能与后端 TiDB 数据库的服务异常有关。\n   \n2. **受影响的上游服务**:\n   - `Frontend` 和 `CheckoutService` 因与 `ProductCatalogService` 的依赖关系受到波及，出现大量延迟和超时错误。\n\n3. **错误模式**:\n   - `Region is unavailable` 以及 `HTTP 状态码 500 错误`，表明 TiDB 的某些分区出现问题，可能是分区崩溃或重启中。\n\n下一步建议继续深入分析 TiDB 的监控指标以验证根因。需要吗？"}
